<h1>Booking Cancelled</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @user.full_name %> and <%= @friend.user.full_name %>,</p>

<p>The following booking has been cancelled:</p>

<div style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 5px;">
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @booking.start_time.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @booking.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> - <%= @booking.end_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></p>
  <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= @booking.duration %> hours</p>
  <p><strong>Service Category:</strong> <%= @booking.service_category.name %></p>
</div>

<p>The time slot has been released and is now available for new bookings.</p>

<p>If you'd like to schedule a new booking, please visit our website to see available time slots.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The Rent A Friend Team
</p>
